<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Two joining fragments (a. approx. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.31</measure>), and a third (b.) possibly from the same monument, from a <rs type="material">white marble</rs> feature with a smooth, long, inscibed fascia, with mouldings above and below; the lower moulding is also the bottom of the feature—perhaps a  low <rs type="objectType" cert="low">statue base</rs> or a <rs type="objectType" cert="low">statue base capital</rs>.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p> Inscribed in two lines on the fascia.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Description of Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.02</measure>; ligatured <foreign lang="grc">ΤΕ</foreign> in a. l. 1.</p>
</div>

